data.description: Price reduced for a quick sale Beautiful 3bedroom 1 1/2 bath home, master bath with separate tub and shower, two stories, all bedrooms upstairs, 2 car garage attached, washer and dryer in garage, forced air and heat, kitchen dining area and living room downstairs, ceramic tile throughout home, master bedroom with a balcony, front street view with a little yard, community pool, security gate, Close to 91 fwy,603 fwy, 710 fwy.
